b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":1087,"category_name":"Events","pr_category_id":"4","title_name":"New Void Enemy and Void Battle Limited-Time Endeavors!","message":"<div>A new Void enemy was added to Void Battles (event quests where you can battle powerful boss enemies) at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1582178400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>You can craft new weapons using the materials obtained by defeating the newly added Void enemy.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Furthermore, Limited Void Battle Endeavors will be available between <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1582178400\\"><\/span> and <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1582869599\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/ae98c6183f1cb78f7c8da1ed82f96c5d.png\\"><\/div><div>A chimera possessed by an insatiable loathing has absorbed black mana, lending even greater power to the flames of hatred that char its body. Its maddening breath sucks the light from the living, leaving them a husk of their former selves that will eventually succumb to their own malice.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0New Void Enemy<\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/42f216ee2ec87a33b06c1dec90eb9392.png\\"><\/div><div>Ebon Chimera (Shadow), Required Might: 13,000<\/div><div>With its two powerful abilities, Overgrowth and Frenzy, this mighty foe grows more and more dangerous as the fight rages on! You&#39;ll also need to watch out for the poison and blindness afflictions.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Crafting<\/div><div>Void weapons that can be crafted using materials obtained from the Ebon Chimera have been added.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>You must have first obtained specific weapons before you can craft weapons using materials obtained from the Ebon Chimera.<\/div><div>The required weapons are the shadow-attuned 5\\u2605 weapons that can be crafted using materials obtained from the Proud Manticore.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The weapon that is required differs based on the weapon type for the weapon you wish to craft. You can check the requirements by selecting Materials for the Ebon Chimera weapons on the Craft tab under Crafting.<\/div><div>Note: Weapons crafted using materials obtained from the Ebon Chimera cannot be dismantled.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>These weapons are the only Void weapons that surpass the core weapons in terms of strength.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>What&#39;s more, weapons such as Soul Crusher, which can be crafted using materials obtained from the Eolian Phantom, can now be enhanced into light-attuned weapons with the Ebon Chimera&#39;s Bane and Frenzy Res abilities. Additionally, blades and daggers have been added to weapon types you can craft using materials obtained from the Eolian Phantom.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Void Battles Schedule<\/div><div>You can play Void Battles anytime, regardless of the day of the week. However, the Void enemies that appear will differ based on the day. Check out the Void Battles Schedule notification for information about when each Void enemy is scheduled to appear.<\/div><div><a href=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.com\/en\/news\/detail\/19999\\">Void Battles Schedule<\/a><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Limited Void Battle Endeavors<\/div><div>We&#39;re adding Limited-Time Void Battle Endeavors, separated into Daily and Limited variations. You can complete the endeavors to obtain various rewards.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Limited Void Battle Endeavors Duration<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1582178400\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1582869599\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. For more information about Void Battles, tap Quests on the Home page, then go to the Void Battles page and select Help.<\/div><div>2. For more information about Void enemies, tap Quests on the Home page, then go to the Void Battles page and check Details on the various quest pages.<\/div><div>3. You can check the Endeavors added for a limited time by tapping Endeavors on the Home page, then selecting the Daily or Limited tabs.<\/div><div>4. Players must have completed up to Chapter 7 \/ 5-6 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to participate in Void Battles.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div>","start_time":1582178400,"prev_article_id":"1085","next_article_id":"1075","image_path":"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/ae98c6183f1cb78f7c8da1ed82f96c5d.png","update_time":1581673868}}}'